Homepage: https://github.com/google/snappy

Package: libsnappy
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Architecture: ARCH
Depends: libc (>= 1.1.8), ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: a compression/decompression library
 Snappy is a compression/decompression library. It does not aim for maximum
 compression, or compatibility with any other compression library; instead,
 it aims for very high speeds and reasonable compression.
 .
 This package provides the shared library libsnappy.

Package: libsnappy-dev
Section: libdevel
Provides: snappy-dev
Priority: optional
Architecture: ARCH
Depends: libsnappy (= ${binary:Version}), gcc-dev
Description: Development headers and libsnappy static library
 This package provides libsnappy.a, headers and pkgconfig data required
 to build applications, libraries or plugins using the Snappy API.
